               <p>ii. l. 1,  <foreign xml:lang="grc">
                     <supplied reason="lost">Νυμφάων τ</supplied>έμενος</foreign> cj. Feissel</p>
               <p>ii. l. 2,  The initial <foreign xml:lang="grc">Α</foreign> in <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ἀφροδισίαδος</foreign> is written <foreign xml:lang="grc">Λ</foreign>. and the remaining traces of the first <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ο</foreign> look more like an <foreign xml:lang="grc">Α</foreign>.</p>
               <p>ii. l. 3,  <foreign xml:lang="grc">
